 "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011601, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, the month of Ramazan has indeed arrived. O Allah, the Lord of the month of Ramazan in which You revealed the Holy Quran and made it a sign of guidance and criterion. O Allah, bless us all in this month of Ramazan and help us in fasting in it and that we pray in it and accept our deeds.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Baare Ilaaha yeh Mahe Ramazan jo aa gaya, ay Khuda ay Parwardigaar Mahe Ramazan keh jis mein Tu ne Qur’an naazil kiya aur qaraar diya usko hidaayat ki waazeh (clear) nishani aur haq o baatil mein farq karne waala. Khuda wanda! Pas Tu Mahe Ramazan mein hamein barkat ataa farma aur hamari madad farma keh ham roze rakkhe aur namaze padhe aur hamare aamaal ko qabool farma.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! یقینًا رمضان کا مہینہ آگیا ہے اے معبود! اے ماہِ رمضان کے پروردگار جس میں تو نے قرآن کریم نازل کیا اور تو نے اس کوہدایت کی نشانیاں اور حق وباطل میں فرق کرنے والا بنایا اے معبود! پس ماہ رمضان میں ہم پر برکت نازل فرما اور اس میں روزوں، نمازوں کے لئے ہماری مد د کر اور انہیں ہم سے قبول فرما۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNA-HU QAD DA-KHALA SHAHRO RAMAZAAN. ALLAAHUMMA RABBA SHAHRE RAMAZAA-NAL LAZEE AN-ZALTA FEE-HIL QURAANA WA JA-A’L-TA-HU BAIYYE-NAA-TIM MENAL HODAA WAL FUR-QAAN. ALLAAHUMMA FA-BAARIK LA-NAA FEE SHAHRE RAMAZAANA WA A-I’NNAA A’LAA SE-YAAME-HI WA SALAATE-HI WA TA-QABBAL-HO MINNAA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّهٗ قَدْ دَخَلَ شَهْرُ رَمَضَانَ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ رَبَّ شَهْرِ رَمَضَانَ الَّذِي اَنْزَلْتَ فِيْهِ الْقُرْآنَ وَجَعَلْتَهٗ بَيِّنَاتٍ مِّنَ الْهُدٰى وَالْفُرْقَانِ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ فَبَارِكْ لَنَا فِيْ شَهْرِ رَمَضَانَ وَاَعِنَّا عَلٰى صِيَامِهٖ وَصَلَاتِهٖ وَتَقَبَّلْهُ مِنَّا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlue